    • HawkerStall

      public HawkerStall(Long id, String thumbnail, String name, Long rating, String hawkercentrename, String unitno, String operationhours, Long communityrating, Long noofrating, Long originalcommunityrating, String highlightitems, String foodcategories, double latitude_hc, double longitude_hc, String photourl, String q1_cleaningstartdate, String q1_cleaningenddate, String q2_cleaningstartdate, String q2_cleaningenddate, String q3_cleaningstartdate, String q3_cleaningenddate, String q4_cleaningstartdate, String q4_cleaningenddate, String neighbourhood, boolean healthy)
      Parameters:
      id - Id of hawkerstall
      thumbnail - link for image of hawkerstall
      name - name of hawkerstall
      rating - rating of hawkerstall
      hawkercentrename - name of hawkercentre
      unitno - unit number
      operationhours - operation hours of hawkerstall
      communityrating - community rating of hawkerstall
      noofrating - number of rating received
      originalcommunityrating - original community rating
      highlightitems - highlighted items of the hawkerstall
      foodcategories - the food items sold in hawkerstall
      latitude_hc - latitude of hawkerstall
      longitude_hc - longitude of hawkerstall
      photourl - url of photo
      q1_cleaningstartdate - cleaning start date for first quarter
      q1_cleaningenddate - cleaning end date for first quarter
      q2_cleaningstartdate - cleaning start date for second quarter
      q2_cleaningenddate - cleaning end date for second quarter
      q3_cleaningstartdate - cleaning start date for third quarter
      q3_cleaningenddate - cleaning end date for third quarter
      q4_cleaningstartdate - cleaning start date for fourth quarter
      q4_cleaningenddate - cleaning end date for fourth quarter
      neighbourhood - neighbourhood of the hawkerstall
      healthy - if the hawkerstall has healthy items
